memberdef.name: new_trie_engine
memberdef.initializer: { \ new_struct(TR_ENGINE, TYPE_TR_ENGINE, SIZEOF_TR_ENGINE); \ TrEngine_trie(TR_ENGINE) = NULL; \ TrEngine_memory(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_tries(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_entries(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_nodes(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_memory_max(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_tries_max(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_entries_max(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ TrEngine_nodes_max(TR_ENGINE) = 0; \ }

memberdef.name: new_trie_node
memberdef.initializer: { \ new_struct(TR_NODE, TYPE_TR_NODE, SIZEOF_TR_NODE); \ TrNode_entry(TR_NODE) = ENTRY; \ TrNode_parent(TR_NODE) = PARENT; \ TrNode_child(TR_NODE) = CHILD; \ TrNode_next(TR_NODE) = NEXT; \ TrNode_previous(TR_NODE) = PREVIOUS; \ INCREMENT_NODES(CURRENT_TRIE_ENGINE); \ INCREMENT_MEMORY(CURRENT_TRIE_ENGINE, SIZEOF_TR_NODE); \ }

memberdef.name: new_trie_hash
memberdef.initializer: { \ new_struct(TR_HASH, TYPE_TR_HASH, SIZEOF_TR_HASH); \ TrHash_mark(TR_HASH) = NULL; \ TrHash_num_buckets(TR_HASH) = NUM_BUCKETS; \ new_hash_buckets(TR_HASH, NUM_BUCKETS); \ TrHash_num_nodes(TR_HASH) = NUM_NODES; \ INCREMENT_MEMORY(CURRENT_TRIE_ENGINE, SIZEOF_TR_HASH); \ }

memberdef.name: new_hash_buckets
memberdef.initializer: { \ int i; \ void **ptr; \ new_struct(ptr, void *, NUM_BUCKETS * sizeof(void *)); \ TrHash_buckets(TR_HASH) = (TYPE_TR_NODE **)ptr; \ for (i = NUM_BUCKETS; i != 0; i--) \ *ptr++ = NULL; \ INCREMENT_MEMORY(CURRENT_TRIE_ENGINE, (NUM_BUCKETS)*SIZEOF_TR_BUCKET); \ }

memberdef.name: expand_auxiliary_term_stack
memberdef.initializer: { \ YAP_Term *aux_stack; \ YAP_Int aux_size = CURRENT_AUXILIARY_TERM_STACK_SIZE * sizeof(YAP_Term); \ new_struct(aux_stack, YAP_Term, aux_size * 2); \ memmove(aux_stack, AUXILIARY_TERM_STACK, aux_size); \ free_struct(AUXILIARY_TERM_STACK); \ AUXILIARY_TERM_STACK = aux_stack; \ CURRENT_AUXILIARY_TERM_STACK_SIZE *= 2; \ }

memberdef.name: INCREMENT_MEMORY
memberdef.initializer: { \ TrEngine_memory(TR_ENGINE) += SIZE; \ if (TrEngine_memory(TR_ENGINE) > TrEngine_memory_max(TR_ENGINE)) \ TrEngine_memory_max(TR_ENGINE) = TrEngine_memory(TR_ENGINE); \ }
